message:
fix: correct typings path in package.json

Currently `types` property of package.json points to non-existing file, this change fixes this.
feat: ðŸŽ¸ update button to use pressable
add github issue template + remove duplicate config in package.json
revert text align style + update @types/react-native version

Added Carousel component (#57)

* Added Carousel Component

- Known bugs: When 'itemsPerPage' is set to any number other than 1 and there are not Carousel.Item enough to fill a page, scroll to the last item will not change 'selectedPage'

* some Carousel adjustments

Default props can be set on theme (#63)

* Some common props types, typed theme and types fixes

* Fixed some types

- Fixed some types
- Text support to fontFamily
- Components like Button/Header/Input/Tag accepts all Text props

* Some little fixes

* Make Input's 'selectionColor' prop get value from theme

* Just some little TS fixes

* better support for customization, including fontFamily on Text and Input

* increase useDefaultProps hook use

- Example app improved
- useDefaultProps are used on most components (not used only on Class Components, like Fab and Mention)

* Header simplified and some little visual adjustments

* Example app visual adjustments and Avatar fontWeight 'bold'

* Just removing some unused variables

* Little fixes

* Update useDefaultProps.ts

Just cleaning code

* Update useDefaultProps.ts

A better typing for contributors. Now, props set on defaultProps can't be undefined.
Props coming from useDefaultProps will be different from props received by component.

better theming support (#69)

* Some common props types, typed theme and types fixes

* Fixed some types

- Fixed some types
- Text support to fontFamily
- Components like Button/Header/Input/Tag accepts all Text props

* Just some little TS fixes

* better theming

- removed unused font files
- components now use useTheme hook, instead of useContext(ThemeContext)
- added theme change support again (ThemeContext setTheme)
- example app dark theme
- theme colors now can reference another theme colors (example: colors: { color1: '#000', color2: 'color1'})
- theme.components now accepts only optional properties (minus 'variant' and 'children' props)
- theme.component variants (inherits props from theme.components.[componentName] and add variant props over it)
fix input styling + fix snack initialize bug
add deepmerge and validate in docs

Enhancement: Ability to stack multiple snackbars (#79)

* add paddingStart and borderStartWidth props

* add multiple container feature

* add snackbar containers
